about.history: Our Lady of Lourdes Shrine in Chetpet has been a beacon of faith for over 125 years. Established in 1899, this sacred place has witnessed countless miracles, answered prayers, and has been a source of spiritual comfort for thousands of devotees.
about.mission: To provide a sacred space where all people can encounter the love and healing presence of Our Lady of Lourdes, fostering spiritual growth, community service, and devotion to the Blessed Virgin Mary.
about.vision: To be a center of pilgrimage that inspires faith, promotes healing, and serves as a beacon of hope for all who seek the intercession of Our Lady of Lourdes in their spiritual journey.
